I/O, Directory structures, File names

/hps/nobackup/flicek/ensembl/genebuild/transcriptomic_assessment/metadata_qc/<taxon_id>/<run_accession>

METADATA
Input: list of run accessions in text on filesystem
/hps/nobackup/flicek/ensembl/genebuild/transcriptomic_assessment/metadata_qc//<taxon_id>/run_accessions.txt
Output: json metadata file on filesystem
/hps/nobackup/flicek/ensembl/genebuild/transcriptomic_assessment/metadata_qc//<taxon_id>/<run_accession>/metadata.json (check name of this file)

FASTQ files
Input: run accession to create query
Output: fastq files on file system
/hps/nobackup/flicek/ensembl/genebuild/transcriptomic_assessment/metadata_qc/<taxon_id>/<run_accession>/<run_accession>_1.fastq
AND
/hps/nobackup/flicek/ensembl/genebuild/transcriptomic_assessment/metadata_qc/<taxon_id>/<run_accession>/<run_accession>_2.fastq

FASTQC
Input: fastq files on filesystem (from above)
Output: fastqc output files 
/hps/nobackup/flicek/ensembl/genebuild/transcriptomic_assessment/metadata_qc/<taxon_id>/<run_accession>/fastqc/<files?> (check names of files needed)

SUBSAMPLE
Input: fastq files on filesystem (from above)
Output: subsampled fastq files on filesystem 
/hps/nobackup/flicek/ensembl/genebuild/transcriptomic_assessment/metadata_qc/<taxon_id>/<taxon_id>/<run_accession>/<run_accession>_1.fastq.sub
AND
/hps/nobackup/flicek/ensembl/genebuild/transcriptomic_assessment/metadata_qc/<taxon_id>/<taxon_id>/<run_accession>/<run_accession>_2.fastq.sub

(NOTE: you can specify the output filenames or the default will appened "sub" to the filenames, see code: https://github.com/Ensembl/ensembl-anno/blob/a8764837454ce984e294e8d9aaae45a30958deab/support_scripts/subsample_fastq.py#L145)

STAR
Input: subsampled fastq files on filesystem (from above)
Output: STAR directory/ subdirectories/ files
/hps/nobackup/flicek/ensembl/genebuild/transcriptomic_assessment/metadata_qc/<taxon_id>/<run_accession>/star/<files?> (check names of files needed)